  "response": "Some of the best neighborhoods in Chicago include:\n\n1. Lincoln Park\n- Beautiful tree-lined streets\n- Great parks and lakefront access\n- Close to downtown\n- Mix of historic and modern homes\n\n2. Wicker Park\n- Trendy and hip\n- Great restaurants and nightlife\n- Artistic community\n- Popular with young professionals\n\n3. River North\n- Upscale area\n- Excellent dining and entertainment\n- Close to downtown\n- Many high-rise condos\n\n4. Streeterville\n- Lakefront location\n- Near Michigan Avenue\n- Close to museums and Navy Pier\n- Luxury high-rise living\n\n5. Bucktown\n- Trendy neighborhood\n- Artistic atmosphere\n- Great shopping and dining\n- Mix of young professionals\n\n6. Old Town\n- Historic neighborhood\n- Beautiful Victorian homes\n- Close to downtown\n- Vibrant entertainment scene\n\n7. Gold Coast\n- Upscale historic district\n- Luxury shopping\n- Elegant architecture\n- Beautiful mansions\n\n8. Logan Square\n- Up-and-coming neighborhood\n- Affordable housing\n- Great restaurants\n- Strong community feel\n\nEach neighborhood offers unique characteristics, so the \"best\" depends on individual preferences and lifestyle.",
